data.description: BRING ALL OFFERS-This fabulous 3 bed/2 bath home is incredibly full of color and charm.  It is so artsy. Large primary bedroom which goes out to a giant back yard -two fire pits- and a water feature to relax by. Covered patio porch, fenced yard  and corner lot. The house is gorgeous with epoxy flooring in the bathroom, cool looking shower door, wonderful sinks in the bathrooms. Plus the kitchen has a very large farmers sink.  On demand water tank-This home will sing to you schedule a time to see it.
